message.content: "cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR". The paper discusses visual question answering, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is "cs.CV" (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a method for learning textual representations using convolutional neural networks, which falls under "cs.CL" (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves deep learning techniques, which could fall under "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) or "cs.LG" (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper evaluates textual representation methods, which could fall under "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval).
